# AtoZ Cedric Enhanced

A Tampermonkey script for Amazon AtoZ that provides enhanced time tracking and automatic schedule management.

## Features
- Automatic time tracking and calculations
- Customizable work hours and break times
- Real-time remaining time display
- Automatic schedule button detection
- Color-coded time status indicators
- Multiple display format options

## Installation
1. Install Tampermonkey for [Chrome](https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/tampermonkey/dhdgffkkebhmkfjojejmpbldmpobfkfo) or [Firefox](https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/tampermonkey/)
2. Visit the [installation page](https://YOUR-USERNAME.github.io/AtoZCedricEnhanced/)
3. Click the "Install" button

## Usage
After installation, the script will automatically run when you visit AtoZ. You can:
- Set your work hours
- Set your break time
- Choose display format
- View remaining time
- Auto-click schedule buttons

## Updates
The script will automatically check for updates. You can also manually update by reinstalling from the installation page.

## Support
For issues or suggestions, please open an issue in this repository.

